Subject: [PATCH 4/4] sample: wolfip_tap_echo (native_sim + TAP)

TCP + UDP echo server sample bound to 192.0.2.1:4242, runnable under
native_sim against a TAP interface. Demonstrates wolfip_attach_iface +
wolfip_ctrl_set_addr boot wiring. Depends on patches 0001 + 0002.

---

